<p><b>Plumpy'nut</b>, also known as <b>Plumpy</b>, is a <a href="/wiki/Peanut" title="Peanut">peanut</a>-based <a href="/wiki/Food" title="Food">food</a> for use in <a href="/wiki/Famine_relief" title="Famine relief">famine relief</a> which was formulated in 1999 by <a href="/wiki/Andr%C3%A9_Briend" title="André Briend">André Briend</a>, a <a href="/wiki/France" title="France">French</a> <a href="/wiki/Scientist" title="Scientist">scientist</a>.</p>
